-- Ford: sales up "dramatically" on cash for clunkers
-- 
-- Thu Jul 30, 2009 12:13pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/07/30/retire-us-ford-sales-idUSTRE56T4JZ20090730

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Ford Motor Co's ( F.N ) U.S. sales chief said on Thursday that the pace of auto sales has picked up "dramatically" since the launch of a cash for clunkers program. 

 * U.S. sales chief says automaker's July sales were 'strong' before launch of incentive program * U.S. sales chief says industry-wide July sales rate could top 10 million units, highest rate of the year